metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Dirt is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Dirt has sections analyzed in the following keys: A Major,  and D Major.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: The first two chords are from F# major key but I thought it would be stupid to put the entire section in F# when everything after that is in A major. I think why it works is the the fact that F# minor is the relative key to A major bc otherwise the keys are not that closely related.
